704033f-a.title: Brooklyn: Duffield Street - Myrtle Avenue
704033f-a.text:
Duffield Street, north from Myrtle Avenue, seen from under
neath the Myrtle Avenue ''El.''
October 1E, 1940
P. L. Sperr
vO REPRODUCTIONS

704035f-b.title: Brooklyn: Duffield Street - Myrtle Avenue
704035f-b.text:
Duf:ield Street, south from Ayrtle Avenue. On the left is the
Antioch Baptist -hurch and on the right the St. Boniface Church.
View 2 shows the Antioch bhurch, looking north toward Myrtle
Avenue.
P. L. -perr  June 28, 1941
